Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.93,0:00:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: I can't believe\Nyou two are going
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,on a Friendship Quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.01,0:00:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What do ya mean, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.71,0:00:10.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been on one\Ntogether before.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.74,0:00:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.71,0:00:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first time\Nthe map has teamed up
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.31,0:00:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the same ponies for\Na second quest!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.98,0:00:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That {\i1}is{\i0} special!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.92,0:00:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh. Must be 'cause we're extra good\Nat solvin' friendship problems.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.46,0:00:23.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Twilight: I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause it looks like this one\Nmight be a little tricky.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to\Nthe Peaks of Peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.53,0:00:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The... Peaks of... P-P-P-Peril!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.33,0:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, it's just a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.00,0:00:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.24,0:00:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how Cloudsdale\Nis in the clouds,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.31,0:00:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,and the Crystal Empire\Nis made of crystal?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.71,0:00:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair point.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So what can you tell us\Nabout the place, Twilight?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.38,0:00:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Only what Rockhoof told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.95,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Back in his day, nopony knew\Nmuch about the Peaks of Peril.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.32,0:00:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Except for the legend on\Nthis ancient shield.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.19,0:00:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It says a group called the\NKirin used to live there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:00:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,known for their kindness\Nand truth-speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.79,0:01:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we know why\Nthe map called us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.70,0:01:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, other\Ncreatures also lived there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.83,0:01:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nirik. Fearsome beasts\Nof pure fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.74,0:01:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[shudder] Maybe...you should go\Ninstead of me, Twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.18,0:01:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.61,0:01:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Flanks don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.45,0:01:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, I'm sure the two of us'll\Nget that friendship problem
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.15,0:01:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,solved, no matter what\Nkinda creature has it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.17,0:02:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess nopony else is goin'\Nout as far as we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.41,0:02:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they know\Nsomething we don't..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.04,0:02:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Now Fluttershy, I've\Ntold you a dozen times!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.18,0:02:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing\Nto be scared--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.75,0:02:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,[old pony's voice]\NI'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.79,0:02:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You really startled us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh it's just that I'm not\Nused to seeing anypony
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.13,0:02:42.40,Default,,0,0,0,,taking the train to...\Nthe end of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.50,0:02:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,[ominous]\NThe final destination.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The last stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.34,0:02:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We get the picture. Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing but uncharted terrain\Nand wild beasts out that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.39,0:03:13.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, maybe there's a little\Nsomethin' to be scared of.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.76,0:03:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Eeyah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.67,0:03:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Those must be the\NPeaks of Peril. Phew.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.18,0:03:38.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough goin', huh\NFluttersh-- Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.15,0:03:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Agh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.09,0:03:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.57,0:03:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,There. That should be enough\Nflowers to keep your tree cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.24,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.44,0:04:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doin'!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.28,0:04:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,This is no time for\Nvisitin' varmints!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,We're on a friendship\Nquest, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.52,0:04:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, but actual--\N-Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.89,0:04:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,We're burnin' daylight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but what I\Nfound out is that--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.36,0:04:17.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, we gotta get up that peak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure if we use some\Nrope and elbow grease,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.43,0:04:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,we can make it up half--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.23,0:04:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,APPLEJACK! CAN YOU\NPLEASE LISTEN TO ME?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.40,0:04:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[Ahem] What I'm\Ntrying to say is,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.60,0:04:29.43,Default,,0,0,0,,the squirrels told me\Na short cut they take
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,to the Kirin village.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Heh heh.\NSorry, Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.21,0:04:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I s'pose I got a little too\Ncaught up in the adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't come\Nback to get me,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.85,0:04:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably would've talked\Nto the squirrels all day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.37,0:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[rustling]\NI hope that's not a Nirik..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.47,0:05:07.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Show yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.82,0:05:18.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Applejack, and this\Nhere is Fluttershy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.46,0:05:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have any friendship\Nproblems, we're here to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Quiet bunch,\Nain't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.27,0:05:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We're from Equestria.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.47,0:05:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're plum-tickled\Nto meet y'all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.11,0:05:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.75,0:05:48.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What are {\i1}your{\i0} names?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.02,0:05:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,APPLEJACK.\NFLUTTERSHY. Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they don't\Nunderstand us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.49,0:06:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.43,0:06:02.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.96,0:06:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ponish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.03,0:06:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! But you\Ndon't speak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.07,0:06:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't or won't?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.38,0:06:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you excuse\Nus for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.75,0:06:22.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to ask "yes or no"\Nquestions, or they won't answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:24.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Like talkin' to\NAngel bunny?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.89,0:06:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Not exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I can always tell\Nwhat Angel is feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But these Kirin,\Ndon't show anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.06,0:06:35.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how are we gonna\Nsolve a friendship problem
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,if none of 'em will\Ntell us what it IS?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.78,0:06:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,These Kirin are quieter than\Nan apple blossom on snowfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Still. There's gotta be some\Nway to make 'em speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.29,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Beautiful day,\Nain't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.36,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Knock knock!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Now you say "who's there?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.27,0:07:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Police!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.40,0:07:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Police who?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.17,0:07:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,POLICE say somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.38,0:07:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh oh. I feel a\Nsneeze comin' on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.65,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,ACHOOOO!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.85,0:07:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy:\NGesundheit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.35,0:07:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.52,0:07:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ANY of y'all talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we're gettin' somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.53,0:07:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A dark spooky path that\Nleads into unknown territory!?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.03,0:07:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell ya what,\Nsugarcube.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.30,0:07:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You stay and see if\Nyou can get anything
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.17,0:07:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,out of these here Kirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go try to find\None that talks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.81,0:07:58.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! Be careful! And\Nwatch out for Niriks!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.16,0:08:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.13,0:08:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.20,0:08:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Aaah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Have you seen a\NKirin that talks?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.40,0:08:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Any idea where\NI should look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.41,0:08:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, for the love\Nof Celestia!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.54,0:08:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you just\Nsay SOMETHIN'?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[laugh] Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, sorry but\Nthat was too good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you don't know\Nhow much I miss jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,HI-larity! Am I\Npronouncing that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.05,0:08:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Some words I haven't said\Nin a wil.. While.. While.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi, I'm Autumn Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.59,0:08:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You've just arrived and perhaps\Nyou're tired or hungry,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.30,0:08:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,or reflective, and want to\Nsleep and eat and journal?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Which you should do! Of\Ncourse. But first, OH! OH!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.10,0:08:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What joy to talk with another\Ncreature, it's been so long!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.64,0:08:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You must tell me\Neverything about you;
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.34,0:08:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,there's so much to\Nsay, so much to DO!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, look at me, I'm going\Non and you haven't seen--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.87,0:09:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean have you seen--?\NWhat am I saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, you haven't,\Nyou just so I will-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That was somethin', all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.29,0:09:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.96,0:09:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,This.. is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.26,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you think so too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.50,0:09:25.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The way the light shimmers\Noff everything like...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.83,0:09:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like it all suddenly woke\Nup the moment you saw it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.97,0:09:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and you realize maybe the water\Nand the mountains and the forest
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and the, yes the rainbow\Nand the stars and the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.87,0:09:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,are all looking back at you\Nthinking the same thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That we are a part\Nof the everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.78,0:09:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That maybe there's just one\Nthing, and we are all it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.05,0:09:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna say "it's\Npretty," but yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.72,0:09:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha ha ha! [sniff] Mmmmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And this is just the\Nfirst stop on a journey
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,of amazing things to see,\Nsmell, tiptoe through!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.16,0:09:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh I haven't been able to share all\Nof this with anypony in forever,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.16,0:09:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,since they all took\Nthat vow of silence,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.07,0:10:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,so it's a lot for me to, you\Nknow, PROcess. Pro-CESS.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Er. Deal with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa, there...\NVow of silence?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.24,0:10:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That's uh, that's why\Nthey asked me to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.91,0:10:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it's not a sore subject,\Nbut you mind explaining
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.21,0:10:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,why y'all went quiet\Nin the first place?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.22,0:10:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[sigh] You'd rather not\Ntalk about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No.\N-I under--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather SIIIIIIIING!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.23,0:10:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ La, lalalalala lalala,{\i0}\N{\i1} lalala LAAAAAA! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.73,0:10:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ the Kirin used to speak and sing\Nwe weren't always quiet ♪ {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ we told stories and funny jokes\Nmy stand-up was a riot. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.71,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ but then one day a\Nfight broke out ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.25,0:10:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}   ♪ and hurtful words were said ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.51,0:10:51.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ flaring tempers were inflamed\Ndestruction quickly spread ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.99,0:10:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}  ♪ and flaming red from head to\Nhead even burnt our.. bread! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.39,0:10:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I forgot how\Nmuch I love rhyming!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.16,0:10:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Where was I? OH RIGHT!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.03,0:11:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪  my happy village lay in ruins,\Nrelationships got worse ♪ {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.50,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ spoiler alert: we'd\Nquickly learned ♪ {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ that words could be a curse. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.24,0:11:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ "NO MORE TALKING"\Nyelled our leader ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}  ♪ the last thing said out loud. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.84,0:11:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}   ♪ into the stream of silence\Nwe stepped as a crowd. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.28,0:11:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}  ♪ the water cooled emotions\Nand peace was soon restored ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.65,0:11:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}       ♪ but with no way to\Nspeak my thoughts ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.35,0:11:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ I got super... bored. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.12,0:11:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously. There's\Nonly so long that
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sudoku can keep\Nyou entertained!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.59,0:11:32.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}     ♪ cause rainbows won't\Nlight up the sky ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.59,0:11:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}     ♪ unless you let it rain ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}   ♪ and shiny apples\Nsometimes come with worms. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.87,0:11:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ Though you can't give\Nup your laughter ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}     ♪ cause you're scared of\Na little pain ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.54,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}       ♪ it's a lesson that\Nthe Kirin never learned. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.71,0:11:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I was stuck in silent prison\Nwith the voices in my head ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.15,0:11:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}♪ till I tripped over my salvation\Nin a helpful flower bed ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.79,0:12:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}        ♪ I'd found a cure\Nto clear my pipes ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.06,0:12:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}       ♪ and I became quite\Nchatty ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.29,0:12:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ with years and years\Nof stored up words ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}   ♪ I drove my village batty! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.86,0:12:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}       ♪ They didn't like my\Njokes and songs ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.10,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}     ♪ and daily dose of news ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.37,0:12:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ the plays I wrote, the speeches\Nspoke, variety reviews, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.87,0:12:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}  ♪ or the story about the Kirin\Nwho hid below an opera stage ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,[spoken quickly] and fell in\Nlove with this opera singer
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.94,0:12:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and he wore a freaky half mask\Nthing and played the organ a lot
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.28,0:12:27.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and got all broody because\Nthe singer was in love with
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.08,0:12:30.45,Default,,0,0,0,,another dude so he took her away\Non this underground gondola
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.55,0:12:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, who doesn't\Nlove musical theatre!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.05,0:12:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ The village leader made it clear,\NI had to make my choice ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.73,0:12:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ I could stay and live with them\Nor I could keep my voice ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.16,0:12:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}    ♪ so I came here,\Nbut left the couch alone, ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.07,0:12:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ they're hard to move. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.73,0:12:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1} ♪ With just the view for company\Nuntil you heard me groove! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.17,0:12:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Take it away, boys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.61,0:12:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}       ♪ Cause rainbows won't\Nlight up the sky ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}    ♪  unless you let it rain ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.51,0:13:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}  ♪ and candles just won't\Nglow until they're burned. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.88,0:13:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ though you can't give\Nup your laughter ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ cause you're scared of\Na little pain ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.49,0:13:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}    ♪ it's a lesson that\Nmy village never learned. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.33,0:13:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ No matter how hard\NI schooled them ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.40,0:13:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}      ♪ fear of hurt is still\Nwhat ruled them ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.97,0:13:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}       ♪ sometimes you\Ngotta let it RAIN! ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.68,0:13:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}   ♪  Yeah, sometimes you've\Ngotta let it.. rain. ♪{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.62,0:13:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,No pony should give up\Nfeelin' their feelins,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.85,0:13:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,just to keep from\Ngettin' angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.29,0:13:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Y'know, when I\Nstarted talking again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] I bet this here's the problem\Nthat Fluttershy and I
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.80,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,came to help y'all with!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.30,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Who's Fluttershy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.70,0:13:55.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did you name your shadow!?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.54,0:13:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mine's called Silhouette\NGloom of the Sundown Lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.71,0:14:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Riiiight...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.01,0:14:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm thinking if we just\Ngo talk to the other Kirin,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.28,0:14:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,we can get 'em to welcome\Nyou back proper-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.61,0:14:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe even convince\N'em to take your cure!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Yes, Yes\Nof course!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.52,0:14:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.. Just one\Nsmall thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.72,0:14:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,The antidote from\Nmy anecdote?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.32,0:14:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no cure left!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.13,0:14:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I used the last of the Foal's\NBreath flowers to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And I haven't seen\Nthem bloom since.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.53,0:14:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh. Well, this wouldn't be a\NFriendship Quest if it was easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.40,0:14:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna start by gettin' your\Nfriends to welcome you back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.37,0:14:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You know? Between you and me,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.71,0:14:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure she's\Ngoing to convince them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.21,0:14:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,"Nope."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But... I hope she does.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting] Fluttershy, guess what!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Both: I figured out the\Nfriendship problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.79,0:14:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.76,0:14:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.43,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Bet that's a problem\Nthe Kirin never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:14:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[giggle] No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.77,0:15:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyhow, we gotta get\N'em all talkin' again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no-no-no-no-no!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't EVER let that happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.07,0:15:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you said you figured\Nout the friendship problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.94,0:15:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Was somethin' lost\Nin translation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.15,0:15:15.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kirin are usually\Npeaceful and kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.22,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But when they get mad,\Nthey turn into Niriks,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.75,0:15:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,creatures made of\Nfire and vengeance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That seemed less scary\Nwhen it was in a song.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.43,0:15:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time they all\Nargued, they got so angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.10,0:15:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,they accidentally destroyed\Ntheir whole village!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.90,0:15:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Kirin decided\Nto make sure
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.10,0:15:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,it would never happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.17,0:15:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's no reason\Nto stop talkin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.84,0:15:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.97,0:15:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire is dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.41,0:15:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially in a\Nforest like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.85,0:15:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Think of all the\Nanimals it could hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.38,0:15:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Not if they don't turn\Ninto fire-breathin' Nirik
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.62,0:15:50.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.18,0:15:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And how can you be\Nsure that won't happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.52,0:15:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's gotta be\Na better way
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.12,0:15:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,than givin' up all\Nyour feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.99,0:15:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,APPLEJACK!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.02,0:15:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not LISTENING!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.79,0:16:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Cause you're not\NTALKIN' any sense!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, what\Nare they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.10,0:16:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.60,0:16:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe they got worried because\Nwe were arguing with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, shucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.41,0:16:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just havin' a\Nnormal, civil disagreement.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.38,0:16:16.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Honest!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.61,0:16:18.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they taking us!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.48,0:16:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,To the Stream of Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.45,0:16:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hit that water, we'll\Nnever be able to talk
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.82,0:16:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,or FEEL anything ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.56,0:16:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,[evil voice]\NPUT THEM DOWN!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:39.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right, I\Nthink I know this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.00,0:16:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's tryin' to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.77,0:16:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,[whoosh] Well, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.81,0:16:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't have them silence the\Nonly friend who'll speak to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She talks!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.38,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You have {\i1}no {\i0}idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.91,0:16:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fluttershy, meet Autumn Blaze.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for that,\Num, wall of fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.82,0:17:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But.. I thought Niriks were\Ndangerous when they're angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.96,0:17:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know you could\Ncontrol your temper?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't. I guess anger's\Nlike other feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.90,0:17:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about having them,\Nit's what you do with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And giving up happiness to keep\Naway anger is no kinda life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.04,0:17:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought\Nof it that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.71,0:17:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine not being able\Nto talk to my animal friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.27,0:17:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Fern Flare, you used to\Nlove to laugh at everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.65,0:17:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Rain Shine, you sung the\Nmost beautiful harmonies.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you miss it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.68,0:17:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're worried\Nabout fightin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.62,0:17:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But friends can disagree\Nwithout causin' a ruckus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.69,0:17:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Every pony gets mad sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.96,0:17:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Even Applejack and I argue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.06,0:17:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What? When do\Nwe ever argue?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.40,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem. On the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And about the\NKirin being silent!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And RIGHT NOW!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.37,0:17:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[chuckle] We don't\Nalways see eye-to-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.44,0:17:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But we never let that get in\Nthe way of our friendship.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.21,0:18:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you're really angry,\Nthen take some time away
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.91,Default,,0,0,0,,to be a Nirik where it\Nwon't hurt anypony.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.89,0:18:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they're tryin'\Nto say somethin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.36,0:18:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,OK. Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no! Somekirin\Ntrapped in a well?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.20,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,OK, Baby?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.26,0:18:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby fish?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.10,0:18:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Baby- Baby fish mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.70,0:18:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Something? Anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:23.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah just write it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.47,0:18:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! This is making me furious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.64,0:18:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.11,0:18:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.11,0:18:31.81,Default,,0,0,0,,[roar]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.45,0:18:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You were saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.75,0:18:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! You want the cure for\Nthe Stream of Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.46,0:18:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,That's wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.43,0:18:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Except there aren't any\Nflowers left to make the cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.17,0:18:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.70,0:18:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, beyond sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.07,0:18:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, I've had a\Nlot of alone time lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.27,0:19:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I searched the entire forest\Nseventy three and a half times.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Although I wonder if that second\Nhalf could make a difference..
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.71,0:19:11.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm. I wish she'd told us what kind\Nof flowers she's looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.65,0:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,They're called Foal's Breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.52,0:19:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh Fluttershy?\NA little help?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.40,0:19:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] He says he knows where\Nto find Foals Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.67,0:19:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, what are\Nwe waitin' for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.34,0:19:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.48,0:19:40.61,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] THAT's what Foal's\NBreath looks like!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.81,0:19:43.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Autumn Blaze never would have\Nmade it past the Peaks
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.22,0:19:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,to search here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.95,0:19:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you an apology.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.59,0:19:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.39,0:19:50.09,Default,,0,0,0,,'Cause if your kindness hadn't\Nmade you stop to help
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.19,0:19:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the squirrels, we never would've\Nfound this here flower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.76,0:19:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And if your honesty hadn't\Nconvinced the Kirin to talk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we wouldn't NEED to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh heh. Guess it's a good\Nthing the map sent both of us, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.41,0:20:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasp] You found them!\NWhere were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.51,0:20:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me everything, and\Nfeel free to add
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.81,0:20:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,complicated descriptions\Nand comedic tangents.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.65,0:20:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. First things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.94,0:20:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Autumn Blaze, you\Nhave given us a gift:
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.17,0:20:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,the realization that\Nanger is within us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.24,0:20:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is our choice\Nhow we let it out.
